name: Fallen Feathers Of Firmament
description:
It was said that her fallen feathers rained down to the Earth from the heavens and into the soil. 

Up they rose; fountains pouring forth from below. Fringed crystals combing the air, reflecting the great blue chrysalis above.

Camera: Nikon D90
Lens: Carl Zeiss Jena Biometar 2.8/80
